{"tid":838880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【封殺港獨】昨就倉促聯署致歉未息火 陳沛然今終退建制派聲明","createTime":"2018-09-27T12:50:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T15:02:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b53541ac22cd2ce0fc5505d8091e81010b80d46c","tid":838880,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T12:50:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180927/58731410\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180927%2F58731410&d=0SoPDjFcrTt7RNAzShIFEdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=bd38aea5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180927%2F58731410&h=d321d5d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180927/58731410</a><br />\n<br />\n【封殺港獨】昨就倉促聯署致歉未息火 陳沛然今終退建制派聲明<br />\n<br />\n54分鐘前3.4K<br />\n即時要聞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180927/large/1538049108_5895.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180927%2Flarge%2F1538049108_5895.png&h=cecca18d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n政府本周一刊憲宣布禁止主張港獨的香港民族黨運作，建制派隨即發表聯合聲明，表明堅決反對港獨，並全力支持保安局依據《社團條例》授予的權力取締民族黨，其中以「中間派」自居的醫學界議員陳沛然因參與聯署被選民狂轟。昨天就倉促聯署致歉的陳沛然今日在Facebook宣佈，退出建制派當日發出的的聯合聲明，但重申反對港獨。<br />\n<br />\n陳沛然周一與建制派連成一線聯署後，隨即被真普選醫生聯盟成員黃任匡在網上炮轟，指摘陳作出大事大非的決定前，未有進行民調及諮詢業界意見，質疑陳是否暗地歸邊。陳昨日曾發聲明回應，指自己因為一心反港獨，「倉促同意聯署」，對於「部份同業」的疑慮深表歉意，陳沛然同時重申，會竭力維護香港核心價值和根據《基本法》第27條賦予港人的各項權利和自由。<br />\n<br />\n不過，陳沛然的聲明並未能平息爭議，有網民留言「睇左你篇《澄清》，如果無跟進動作退出聯署，恐怕越澄越唔清」，另有網民指「道歉？醫返都冇用」，黃任匡亦留言要求陳「應該出份公開信，退出聯署，以正視聽」。<br />\n<br />\n事隔一天，陳沛然今日再透過Facebook宣佈，退出建制派在周一發出的的聯合聲明，但重申反對港獨，並指會及竭力維護根 據《基本法》第二十七條賦予港人的各項權利和自由。立法會教育界議員葉建源及歐陽英傑（星屑醫生）like了陳的帖文，其中歐陽英傑留言：「一直對你有信心，你無令我們失望，加油。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n立會補選新聞，《蘋果》一網睇晒<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/appledaily1125\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fappledaily1125&d=0SoPDjFcrTt7RNAzShIFEdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=2e25bc70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/appledaily1125</a>"},{"pid":"09d87359d64d0e335d42ecbfc34da5e4cc83edbe","tid":838880,"uid":103156,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T12:55:45.000Z","msg":"一日共狗，一世共狗"},{"pid":"13d7063b4280c10ea53932fcce9381c477f4aa75","tid":838880,"uid":21545,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T14:05:20.000Z","msg":"知道玩大咗 所以跳船<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fa972583f5ab2ea95a64822cde55aa44d78c33f","tid":838880,"uid":66324,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T14:07:28.000Z","msg":"露底 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e2ca7fd50137121a2a501e3e320a177aa83dd0b","tid":838880,"uid":128369,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T14:10:44.000Z","msg":"所謂中間派咪即建制派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0df55111949572f9ea9fff67ea7ba3d90c69c66d","tid":838880,"uid":31841,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T14:12:49.000Z","msg":"垃圾真係垃圾<br />\n讀咁撚多書原來讀屎片<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc1ba45d431b8dce3b2cdaf42a15ebc6ba033ca","tid":838880,"uid":130105,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9e2ca7fd50137121a2a501e3e320a177aa83dd0b","tid":838880,"uid":128369,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T14:10:44.000Z","msg":"所謂中間派咪即建制派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T15:02:34.000Z","msg":"中間派即係著數派<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}